<p>やがて<span className="vocab">書記<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>書記</rb><rt>しょき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;secretary</span></span>の<span className="vocab">川村<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>川村</rb><rt>かわむら</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Kawamura (name)</span></span>がどうか<span className="vocab">お着席<span className="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>着席</rb><rt>ちゃくせき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;please be seated</span></span>をと<span className="vocab">云う<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>云</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;said</span></span>から、<span className="vocab">柱<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>柱</rb><rt>はしら</rt></ruby>&nbsp;pillar; column</span></span>があって<span className="vocab">靠りかかる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>靠</rb><rt>よ</rt></ruby>りかかる&nbsp;lean against; recline on</span></span>のに<span className="vocab">都合のいい<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>都合</rb><rt>つごう</rt></ruby>のいい&nbsp;convenient</span></span><span className="vocab">所<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>所</rb><rt>ところ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;place; spot</span></span>へ<span className="vocab">坐った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>坐</rb><rt>すわ</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;sat down</span></span>。<span className="vocab">海屋<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>海屋</rb><rt>かいおく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Nukina Kaioku (famous painter and calligrapher from Shikoku; 1778-1863)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">懸物<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>懸物</rb><rt>かけもの</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hanging scroll; painting</span></span>の<span className="vocab">前<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>前</rb><rt>まえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;front (of)</span></span>に<span className="vocab">狸<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>狸</rb><rt>たぬき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Tanuki (nickname for the school principal)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">羽織<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>羽織</rb><rt>はおり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;haori (Japanese half-coat)</span></span>、<span className="vocab">袴<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>袴</rb><rt>はかま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hakama (men's formal pleated skirt)</span></span>で着席すると、<span className="vocab">左<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>左</rb><rt>ひだり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;left (side)</span></span>に<span className="vocab">赤シャツ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>赤</rb><rt>あか</rt></ruby>シャツ&nbsp;Red Shirt (nickname for the head teacher)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">同じく<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>同</rb><rt>おな</rt></ruby>じく&nbsp;likewise; similarly</span></span>羽織袴で<span className="vocab">陣取った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>陣取</rb><rt>じんど</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;took up (his) position</span></span>。<span className="vocab">右<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>右</rb><rt>みぎ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;right (side)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">方<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>ほう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;direction</span></span>は<span className="vocab">主人公<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>主人公</rb><rt>しゅじんこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;the guest of honor</span></span>だというので<span className="vocab">うらなり<span className="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;Uranari (nickname for Koga, the English teacher)</span></span><span className="vocab">先生<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先生</rb><rt>せんせい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;teacher</span></span>、これも<span className="vocab">日本服<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日本服</rb><rt>にほんふく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Japanese dress</span></span>で<span className="vocab">控えて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>控</rb><rt>ひか</rt></ruby>えて&nbsp;be in waiting</span></span>いる。おれは<span className="vocab">洋服<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>洋服</rb><rt>ようふく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Western-style dress</span></span>だから、<span className="vocab">かしこまる<span className="vocabdef">かしこまる&nbsp;sit formally (on one's heels)</span></span>のが<span className="vocab">窮屈<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>窮屈</rb><rt>きゅうくつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;uncomfortable</span></span>だったから、すぐ<span className="vocab">胡坐をかいた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>胡坐</rb><rt>あぐら</rt></ruby>をかいた&nbsp;sat in a cross-legged position</span></span>。<span className="vocab">隣りの<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>隣</rb><rt>とな</rt></ruby>りの&nbsp;next; neighboring</span></span><span className="vocab">体操<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>体操</rb><rt>たいそう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;physical education</span></span><span className="vocab">教師<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>教師</rb><rt>きょうし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;instructor; teacher</span></span>は<span className="vocab">黒<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>黒</rb><rt>くろ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;black</span></span>ずぼんで、ちゃんとかしこまっている。体操の教師だけにいやに<span className="vocab">修行が積んでいる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>修行</rb><rt>しゅうぎょう</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>積</rb><rt>つ</rt></ruby>んでいる&nbsp;be well-trained (in)</span></span>。やがて<span className="vocab">お膳<span className="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>膳</rb><rt>ぜん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(dinner) trays</span></span>が<span className="vocab">出る<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>る&nbsp;appear; be brought out</span></span>。<span className="vocab">徳利<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>徳利</rb><rt>とくり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(saké) bottles (usually <ruby><rb>徳利</rb><rt>とっくり</rt></ruby>)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">並ぶ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>並</rb><rt>なら</rt></ruby>ぶ&nbsp;be lined up</span></span>。<span className="vocab">幹事<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>幹事</rb><rt>かんじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;master of ceremonies</span></span>が<span className="vocab">立って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;rose; stood up</span></span>、<span className="vocab">一言<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一言</rb><rt>いちごん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;a word</span></span><span className="vocab">開会<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>開会</rb><rt>かいかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;opening of an event</span></span>の<span className="vocab">辞<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>辞</rb><rt>じ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;formal remarks</span></span>を<span className="vocab">述べる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>述</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>べる&nbsp;deliver (speech; remarks)</span></span>。それから狸が立つ。赤シャツが<span className="vocab">起つ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>起</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>つ&nbsp;rose; stood up</span></span>。<span className="vocab">ことごとく<span className="vocabdef">ことごとく&nbsp;all; one and all</span></span><span className="vocab">送別<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>送別</rb><rt>そうべつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;farewell</span></span>の辞を述べたが、<span className="vocab">三人共<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>三人共</rb><rt>さんにんとも</rt></ruby>&nbsp;all three (together)</span></span><span className="vocab">申し合せた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>申</rb><rt>もう</rt></ruby>し<ruby><rb>合</rb><rt>あわ</rt></ruby>せた&nbsp;arranged; agreed (upon)</span></span>ようにうらなり<span className="vocab">君<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>くん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(suffix of familiarity for males)</span></span>の、<span className="vocab">良教師<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>良教師</rb><rt>りょうきょうし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;good instructor</span></span>で<span className="vocab">好人物<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>好人物</rb><rt>こうじんぶつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;good-natured person</span></span>な<span className="vocab">事<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;fact; matter</span></span>を<span className="vocab">吹聴して<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吹聴</rb><rt>ふいちょう</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;proclaim; tout</span></span>、<span className="vocab">今回<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今回</rb><rt>こんかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;this time</span></span><span className="vocab">去られる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>去</rb><rt>さ</rt></ruby>られる&nbsp;go away</span></span>のはまことに<span className="vocab">残念<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>残念</rb><rt>ざんねん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;disappointment</span></span>である、<span className="vocab">学校<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>学校</rb><rt>がっこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;school</span></span>としてのみならず、<span className="vocab">個人<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>個人</rb><rt>こじん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;individual (person)</span></span>として大いに<span className="vocab">惜しむ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>惜</rb><rt>お</rt></ruby>しむ&nbsp;regret; be sorry about</span></span>ところであるが、<span className="vocab">ご一身上<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>一身上</rb><rt>いっしんじょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;personal</span></span>の<span className="vocab">ご都合<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>都合</rb><rt>つごう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;circumstances</span></span>で、<span className="vocab">切に<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>切</rb><rt>せつ</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;earnestly; keenly</span></span><span className="vocab">転任<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>転任</rb><rt>てんにん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;transfer</span></span>を<span className="vocab">ご希望<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>希望</rb><rt>きぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;desire</span></span>になったのだから<span className="vocab">致し方がない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>致</rb><rt>いた</rt></ruby>し<ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>かた</rt></ruby>がない&nbsp;nothing can be done (about it)</span></span>という<span className="vocab">意味<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>意味</rb><rt>いみ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;gist; essence</span></span>を述べた。こんな<span className="vocab">嘘<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>嘘</rb><rt>うそ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;lies; falsehoods</span></span>をついて<span className="vocab">送別会<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>送別会</rb><rt>そうべつかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;farewell party</span></span>を<span className="vocab">開いて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>開</rb><rt>ひら</rt></ruby>いて&nbsp;hold; sponsor</span></span>、それでちっとも<span className="vocab">恥かしい<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>恥</rb><rt>はず</rt></ruby>かしい&nbsp;shameful</span></span>とも<span className="vocab">思って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;think; consider</span></span>いない。ことに赤シャツ<span className="vocab">に至って<span className="vocabdef">に<ruby><rb>至</rb><rt>いた</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;as far as</span></span>三人のうちで<span className="vocab">一番<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一番</rb><rt>いちばん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;most (of all)</span></span>うらなり君をほめた。この<span className="vocab">良友<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>良友</rb><rt>りょうゆう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;good friend</span></span>を<span className="vocab">失う<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>失</rb><rt>うしな</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;lose</span></span>のは<span className="vocab">実に<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>実</rb><rt>じつ</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;really; truly</span></span><span className="vocab">自分<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;oneself</span></span>にとって<span className="vocab">大なる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大</rb><rt>だい</rt></ruby>なる&nbsp;great</span></span><span className="vocab">不幸<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>不幸</rb><rt>ふこう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sorrow; grief</span></span>であるとまで云った。しかもその<span className="vocab">いい方<span className="vocabdef">いい<ruby><rb>方</rb><rt>かた</rt></ruby>&nbsp;manner of speaking; choice of words</span></span>がいかにも、もっともらしくって、<span className="vocab">例の<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>例</rb><rt>れい</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;usual; signature</span></span>やさしい<span className="vocab">声<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>声</rb><rt>こえ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;voice</span></span>を<span className="vocab">一層<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>一層</rb><rt>いっそう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;still more</span></span>やさしくして、<span className="vocab">述べ立てる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>述</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>べ<ruby><rb>立</rb><rt>た</rt></ruby>てる&nbsp;elaborate on</span></span>のだから、<span className="vocab">始めて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>めて&nbsp;for the first time</span></span><span className="vocab">聞いた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>聞</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>いた&nbsp;heard</span></span>ものは、<span className="vocab">誰でも<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>誰</rb><rt>だれ</rt></ruby>でも&nbsp;anyone; no matter who</span></span>きっとだまされる<span className="vocab">に極ってる<span className="vocabdef">に<ruby><rb>極</rb><rt>きま</rt></ruby>ってる&nbsp;it's a given that ...</span></span>。マドンナも<span className="vocab">大方<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>大方</rb><rt>おおかた</rt></ruby>&nbsp;probably</span></span>この<span className="vocab">手<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手</rb><rt>て</rt></ruby>&nbsp;method; means</span></span>で<span className="vocab">引掛けた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>引掛</rb><rt>ひっか</rt></ruby>けた&nbsp;ensnared; seduced (a woman)</span></span>んだろう。赤シャツが送別の辞を述べ立てている<span className="vocab">最中<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>最中</rb><rt>さいちゅう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;middle of</span></span>、<span className="vocab">向側<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>向側</rb><rt>むかいがわ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;opposite side</span></span>に坐っていた<span className="vocab">山嵐<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>がおれの顔を<span className="vocab">見て<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;look at</span></span>ちょっと<span className="vocab">稲光<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>稲光</rb><rt>いなびかり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;wink; meaningful glance (lit: lightning)</span></span>をさした。おれは<span className="vocab">返電<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>返電</rb><rt>へんでん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;reply message (lit: reply telegraph)</span></span>として、<span className="vocab">人指し指<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>人指</rb><rt>ひとさ</rt></ruby>し<ruby><rb>指</rb><rt>ゆび</rt></ruby>&nbsp;index finger</span></span>で<span className="vocab">べっかんこうをして<span className="vocabdef">べっかんこうをして&nbsp;pull down on one's lower eyelid (sign of contempt)</span></span>見せた。</p>

