<p>おれはさっきから<span className="vocab">苦しそうに<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>苦</rb><rt>くる</rt></ruby>しそうに&nbsp;looking miserable</span></span><span className="vocab">袴<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>袴</rb><rt>はかま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;hakama (men's formal pleated skirt)</span></span>も<span className="vocab">脱がず<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>脱</rb><rt>ぬ</rt></ruby>がず&nbsp;without taking off; without changing out of</span></span><span className="vocab">控えている<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>控</rb><rt>ひか</rt></ruby>えている&nbsp;show restraint; hold back</span></span><span className="vocab">うらなり<span className="vocabdef">うらなり&nbsp;Uranari (nickname for Koga, the English teacher)</span></span><span className="vocab">君<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>君</rb><rt>くん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(suffix of familiarity for males)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">気の毒<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>の<ruby><rb>毒</rb><rt>どく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;pitiable</span></span>でたまらなかったが、なんぼ<span className="vocab">自分の<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>自分</rb><rt>じぶん</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;one's own</span></span><span className="vocab">送別会<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>送別会</rb><rt>そうべつかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;farewell party</span></span>だって、<span className="vocab">越中褌<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>越中</rb><rt>えっちゅう</rt></ruby><ruby><rb>褌</rb><rt>ふんどし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Etchū loincloth (string waistband)</span></span>の<span className="vocab">裸<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>裸</rb><rt>はだか</rt></ruby>&nbsp;naked</span></span><span className="vocab">踴<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>踴</rb><rt>おどり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;dance</span></span>まで<span className="vocab">羽織<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>羽織</rb><rt>はおり</rt></ruby>&nbsp;haori (Japanese half-coat)</span></span>袴で<span className="vocab">我慢して<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>我慢</rb><rt>がまん</rt></ruby>して&nbsp;endure; put up with</span></span>みている<span className="vocab">必要<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>必要</rb><rt>ひつよう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;necessity</span></span>はあるまいと<span className="vocab">思った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>思</rb><rt>おも</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;thought; considered</span></span>から、そばへ<span className="vocab">行って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>行</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;went (to)</span></span>、<span className="vocab">古賀<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>古賀</rb><rt>こが</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Koga (a.k.a. Uranari)</span></span>さんもう<span className="vocab">帰りましょう<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>帰</rb><rt>かえ</rt></ruby>りましょう&nbsp;let's go home</span></span>と<span className="vocab">退去<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>退去</rb><rt>たいきょ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;leaving; withdrawal</span></span>を<span className="vocab">勧めて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>勧</rb><rt>すす</rt></ruby>めて&nbsp;recommend; counsel</span></span>みた。するとうらなり君は<span className="vocab">今日<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>今日</rb><rt>きょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;today</span></span>は<span className="vocab">私の<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>私</rb><rt>わたし</rt></ruby>の&nbsp;my</span></span>送別会だから、私が<span className="vocab">先<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>先</rb><rt>さき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;first; before</span></span>へ帰っては<span className="vocab">失礼<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>失礼</rb><rt>しつれい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;improper; rude</span></span>です、どうぞ<span className="vocab">ご遠慮なく<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>遠慮</rb><rt>えんりょ</rt></ruby>なく&nbsp;as you please</span></span>と<span className="vocab">動く<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>動</rb><rt>うご</rt></ruby>く&nbsp;move</span></span><span className="vocab">景色<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>景色</rb><rt>けしき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sign; indication</span></span>もない。なに<span className="vocab">構う<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>構</rb><rt>かま</rt></ruby>う&nbsp;matter; be of concern</span></span>もんですか、送別会なら、送別会らしくするがいいです、あの<span className="vocab">様<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>様</rb><rt>さま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;spectacle; scene (= <ruby><rb>有様</rb><rt>ありさま</rt></ruby>)</span></span>を<span className="vocab">ご覧なさい<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>覧</rb><rt>らん</rt></ruby>なさい&nbsp;take a look at</span></span>。<span className="vocab">気狂会<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>気狂会</rb><rt>きちがいかい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;gathering of lunatics</span></span>です。さあ行きましょうと、<span className="vocab">進まない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>進</rb><rt>すす</rt></ruby>まない&nbsp;hesitate</span></span>のを<span className="vocab">無理に<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>無理</rb><rt>むり</rt></ruby>に&nbsp;under compulsion; against one's will</span></span>勧めて、<span className="vocab">座敷<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>座敷</rb><rt>ざしき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;room; parlor</span></span>を<span className="vocab">出かかる<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>出</rb><rt>で</rt></ruby>かかる&nbsp;start to leave; make one's way out</span></span>ところへ、<span className="vocab">野だ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>野</rb><rt>の</rt></ruby>だ&nbsp;Noda (short for Nodaiko, nickname for Yoshikawa, the art teacher)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">箒<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>箒</rb><rt>ほうき</rt></ruby>&nbsp;broom</span></span>を<span className="vocab">振り振り<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>振</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>り<ruby><rb>振</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>り&nbsp;shaking; brandishing</span></span><span className="vocab">進行して来て<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>進行</rb><rt>しんこう</rt></ruby>して<ruby><rb>来</rb><rt>き</rt></ruby>て&nbsp;advanced; came forward</span></span>、や<span className="vocab">ご主人<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>主人</rb><rt>しゅじん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;guest of honor</span></span>が先へ帰るとはひどい。<span className="vocab">日清<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>日清</rb><rt>にっしん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Sino-Japanese</span></span><span className="vocab">談判<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>談判</rb><rt>だんぱん</rt></ruby>&nbsp;negotiations</span></span>だ。帰せないと箒を<span className="vocab">横<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>横</rb><rt>よこ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sideways</span></span>にして行く<span className="vocab">手<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>手</rb><rt>て</rt></ruby>&nbsp;way; means</span></span>を<span className="vocab">塞いだ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>塞</rb><rt>ふさ</rt></ruby>いだ&nbsp;blocked; closed off</span></span>。おれはさっきから<span className="vocab">肝癪が起って<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>肝癪</rb><rt>かんしゃく</rt></ruby>が<ruby><rb>起</rb><rt>おこ</rt></ruby>って&nbsp;temper was aroused</span></span>いるところだから、日清談判なら<span className="vocab">貴様<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>貴様</rb><rt>きさま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;you (condescending)</span></span>は<span className="vocab">ちゃんちゃん<span className="vocabdef">ちゃんちゃん&nbsp;Chinaman</span></span>だろうと、いきなり<span className="vocab">拳骨<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>拳骨</rb><rt>げんこつ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;(clenched) fist; knuckles</span></span>で、野だの<span className="vocab">頭<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>頭</rb><rt>あたま</rt></ruby>&nbsp;head</span></span>を<span className="vocab">ぽかりと喰わして<span className="vocabdef">ぽかりと<ruby><rb>喰</rb><rt>く</rt></ruby>わして&nbsp;thwack someone (on the head)</span></span>やった。野だは<span className="vocab">二三秒<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>二三秒</rb><rt>にさんびょう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;two or three seconds</span></span>の<span className="vocab">間<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>間</rb><rt>あいだ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;interval (time)</span></span><span className="vocab">毒気を抜かれた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>毒気</rb><rt>どっき</rt></ruby>を<ruby><rb>抜</rb><rt>ぬ</rt></ruby>かれた&nbsp;be stunned; be dumbfounded</span></span><span className="vocab">体<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>体</rb><rt>てい</rt></ruby>&nbsp;appearance; air</span></span>で、ぼんやりしていたが、おやこれはひどい。<span className="vocab">お撲ちになったの<span className="vocabdef">お<ruby><rb>撲</rb><rt>ぶ</rt></ruby>ちになったの&nbsp;hitting (a person)</span></span>は<span className="vocab">情ない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>情</rb><rt>なさけ</rt></ruby>ない&nbsp;cruel; coldhearted</span></span>。この<span className="vocab">吉川<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>吉川</rb><rt>よしかわ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yoshikawa (a.k.a. Nodaiko)</span></span>を<span className="vocab">ご打擲<span className="vocabdef">ご<ruby><rb>打擲</rb><rt>ちょうちゃく</rt></ruby>&nbsp;thrashing; beating</span></span>とは<span className="vocab">恐れ入った<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>恐</rb><rt>おそ</rt></ruby>れ<ruby><rb>入</rb><rt>い</rt></ruby>った&nbsp;be taken aback; be astonished</span></span>。いよいよもって日清談判だ。とわからぬ<span className="vocab">事<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>事</rb><rt>こと</rt></ruby>&nbsp;things</span></span>をならべているところへ、うしろから<span className="vocab">山嵐<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>山嵐</rb><rt>やまあらし</rt></ruby>&nbsp;Yama Arashi (nickname for Hotta, the head mathematics teacher)</span></span>が<span className="vocab">何か<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>何</rb><rt>なに</rt></ruby>か&nbsp;something; some kind of</span></span><span className="vocab">騒動<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>騒動</rb><rt>そうどう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;disturbance</span></span>が<span className="vocab">始まった<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>始</rb><rt>はじ</rt></ruby>まった&nbsp;had begun</span></span>と<span className="vocab">見てとって<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>見</rb><rt>み</rt></ruby>てとって&nbsp;understand; perceive</span></span>、<span className="vocab">剣舞<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>剣舞</rb><rt>けんぶ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;sword dance</span></span>をやめて、<span className="vocab">飛んできた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>飛</rb><rt>と</rt></ruby>んできた&nbsp;came running (over)</span></span>が、この<span className="vocab">ていたらく<span className="vocabdef">ていたらく&nbsp;state of affairs</span></span>を見て、いきなり<span className="vocab">頸筋<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>頸筋</rb><rt>くびすじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;scruff of the neck</span></span>をうんと<span className="vocab">攫んで<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>攫</rb><rt>つか</rt></ruby>んで&nbsp;seize; grab by</span></span><span className="vocab">引き戻した<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>引</rb><rt>ひ</rt></ruby>き<ruby><rb>戻</rb><rt>もど</rt></ruby>した&nbsp;pulled backward</span></span>。日清……いたい。いたい。どうもこれは<span className="vocab">乱暴<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>乱暴</rb><rt>らんぼう</rt></ruby>&nbsp;violence; an outrage</span></span>だと<span className="vocab">振りもがく<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>振</rb><rt>ふ</rt></ruby>りもがく&nbsp;struggle; squirm</span></span>ところを横に<span className="vocab">捩ったら<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>捩</rb><rt>ねじ</rt></ruby>ったら&nbsp;twisted</span></span>、<span className="vocab">すとんと<span className="vocabdef">すとんと&nbsp;with a thud</span></span><span className="vocab">倒れた<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>倒</rb><rt>たお</rt></ruby>れた&nbsp;went down; fell</span></span>。あとはどうなったか<span className="vocab">知らない<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>知</rb><rt>し</rt></ruby>らない&nbsp;don't know</span></span>。<span className="vocab">途中で<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>途中</rb><rt>とちゅう</rt></ruby>で&nbsp;on the way (home)</span></span>うらなり君に<span className="vocab">別れて<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>別</rb><rt>わか</rt></ruby>れて&nbsp;parted (from)</span></span>、うちへ帰ったら<span className="vocab">十一時<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>十一時</rb><rt>じゅういちじ</rt></ruby>&nbsp;11 o'clock</span></span><span className="vocab">過ぎ<span className="vocabdef"><ruby><rb>過</rb><rt>す</rt></ruby>ぎ&nbsp;after; past ... (time)</span></span>だった。</p>
